        <span id="att-8642575-description" itemprop="description">poc.js, poc.html, glMatrix-0.9.5.min.js. Extract and use as in note 0.</span></a>
        — <a href="attachment.cgi?id=8642575&amp;action=edit" itemprop="url">Details</a>
